Privacy Policy
Welcome to Cool Fonts - Fancy Letters. Art Maker Studio (the "team", "our", "us" or "we") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard user data in this app.
Information Collection and Use
Our app uses AdMob advertising service, which may collect device information, user behavior data, and advertising identifiers for providing personalized ads.
Advertising Service
We use third-party advertising networks (e.g., AdMob) to display personalized ads to users.
Advertisers' Data Use
Third-party advertising networks (like AdMob) may collect and use user information as per their privacy policies to provide ad services.
Third-Party Links
Our app may contain links to third-party websites or services. Our privacy policy does not apply to those third-party sites.
Policy Updates
We may update the privacy policy from time to time, and the latest version will be posted on this page.
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us.
Contact Us
If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, you may contact us at feedback.to.prime.developer@gmail.com.